## .gitignore patch
## Add these lines to the repository root .gitignore
## (append to the existing file — do not replace it)

# ─── SQLite queue database (runtime state, NOT committed) ────────────────────
data/queue.db
data/queue.db-wal
data/queue.db-shm

# ─── Keep the example schema snapshot committed ───────────────────────────────
# (The example file is an empty DB produced by applying schema.sql;
#  it documents the schema without containing any live state.)
!data/queue.db.example
assets/stock-cache/
